Localhost Installation Instructions:

1. Install Scala
<code>sudo apt-get install scala</code>

2. Install Play
Go to http://www.playframework.com/download and download 2.1.0 or later
Unzip to a convenient location

3. 'cd' to app directory

4. <code>/play_directory/play run</code>

5. Enter "localhost:9000" in a browser address bar